### Change 2: Backend - DataFormsController.cs Manager Resolution (Lines 1290-1326)

**Location**: `MaterialControlCenter/Controllers/DataFormsController.cs`  
**Method**: `GetApprovalChain()` → Manager resolution (role_id 5)

**Before**:
```csharp
if (roleName.Contains("manager") && !roleName.Contains("material"))
{
    // Manager langsung initiator
    var mgr = supChain.ElementAtOrDefault(1);
    if (mgr != null) { resolvedKpks.Add(mgr.Kpk); resolvedNames.Add(mgr.Name ?? mgr.Kpk); }
