## 🔄 Approval Chain Hierarchy Comparison

### SCRAP/TPR (Original Logic - Unchanged)
```
User (Login KPK)
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[0] = User's Supervisor
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[1] = Manager ← Step 1 Manager
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[2] = Director ← Step 3 Director
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[3] = President Director ← Step 4 (from DB rules)
```

### PIA (New Logic - Supervisor's Supervisor)
```
Supervisor Selected by User (Selected KPK)
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[0] = Selected Supervisor (passed as initiatorKpk)
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[1] = Manager (Supervisor's Supervisor) ← Step 1 Manager
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[2] = Director (Manager's Supervisor) ← Step 3 Director
  ↓ supervisor field points to...
supChain[3] = President Director ← Step 4 (from DB rules)
```

