✓ Step 1 (Manager): David Smith (67890) ← From Jane's supervisor
✓ Step 2 (Manager): [From DB rules]
✓ Step 3 (Director): [From supChain[2]]
✓ Step 4 (President Director): [From mcc_approval_rule table]
```

