## 📝 Backward Compatibility

**Fallback Mechanism**:
```javascript
const supervisorKpk = document.getElementById("supervisorInitiatorKpk")?.value?.trim() || initiatorKpk;
```

If `supervisorInitiatorKpk` is not populated (e.g., old forms), system falls back to `initiatorKpk` (original behavior).

**Supported Scenarios**:
- ✅ New forms with supervisor selection
- ✅ Old forms without supervisor field (fallback to initiator)
- ✅ Mixed forms (some fields populated)

